      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just hard to see the point of it all. they're so busy with their own lives, and then they have to come over here and deal with my appointments and all this stuff. if i wasn't around, they could finally just breathe, you know? it feels like the kindest thing i could do for them is to just... stop being a problem.",
